# Table of Contents #

### Imperial Dynasties ###
# Haxâmanahan (First Imperial Dynasty)
# Ardâcheran (Second Imperial Dynasty, cadet of Haxâmanahans)
# Artaxshâsan (Third Imperial Dynasty)
# Phaxsharân (Fourth Imperial Dynasty)
# Aldhrâdan (Fifth Imperial Dynasty)
# Tirdâhan (Sixth Imperial Dynasty, cadet of Aldhrâdans)

### Major Imperial Nobility ###
# Vasnan
# Mahyaran
# Adelez

### Minor Imperial Nobility ###
# Bârdiyen (cadet of Vasnans)
# Ashtadet (cadet of Vasnans)
# Kahlavan
# Bahez
# Karanez

### Non-Imperial Royalty ###
# Barâman (cadet of Ardâcherans)

### Non-Imperial Nobility ###
## Clyan Nobility ##
# Adarfiruzen
# Bahlikaran
# Bahraman
# Caramadran
# Dadfiruzen
# Dahmard
# Esrecarzen
# Farshidzen
# Garozen
# Homazen
# Imez
# Jamo
# Kerhamez
# Khudaradmen
# Lamarzen
# Mentarez
# Namdarez
# Naymardan
# Osard
# Pamaran
# Qudoz
# Ramazen

# Visnarmaken

# WotR Pirate Laamp

### Haxâmanahan ###

lineofhaxamanish1 = {
    name = Haxamanish

    dynasty = dynasty_haxamanahan
    religion = faith_azianic
    culture = khyan

    sexuality = heterosexual

    trait = wrathful
    trait = arrogant
    trait = gregarious

    trait = education_diplomacy_4

    4980.11.28 = {
        birth = yes
    }

    5088.4.11 = {
        death = {
            death_reason = death_natural_causes
        }
    }
}

lineofhaxamanish6 = {
    name = Datuvahya

    dynasty = dynasty_haxamanahan
    religion = faith_azianic
    culture = khyan

    trait = generous
    trait = temperate
    trait = cynical

    martial = 15

    intrigue = 11

    prowess = 13

    trait = education_martial_prowess_2
    trait = physique_good_2

    5137.11.13 = {
        birth = yes
    }

    5172.3.21 = { # Completing the Process his grandfather Dârayavahu I started, Datuvahya lavished upon them and then converted
        religion = faith_arienism
    }

    5191.8.12 = {
        death = {
            death_reason = death_assassination
        }
    }
}

lineofhaxamanish7 = {
    name = Ariyamna

    dynasty = dynasty_haxamanahan
    religion = faith_azianic
    culture = khyan

    father = lineofhaxamanish6

    sexuality = asexual

    trait = chaste
    trait = calm
    trait = content

    learning = 11

    trait = education_learning_4
    trait = twin # identical, for if the DNA's are made

    5154.12.21 = {
        birth = yes
    }

    5172.3.21 = { # Converted with the whole Royal Court
        religion = faith_arienism
    }

    5197.12.22 = { # Became known as the Elder posthumously after his nephew adopted his name as a regnal name
        death = {
            death_reason = death_natural_causes
        }
        give_nickname = nick_the_elder
    }
}
